      "message": "To be clear, the Reason field is removed from the device structure but the data is still being stored.  The idea behind this is instead of having 1 reason field that keeps getting overwritten with the latest reason, we will not have a separate \"device updates\" structure that will keeps all the updates (including reasons) to the device.  Please see the last page at https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sOv5R7iOBTlzXcCVaUfOOzd5617ISQGnseadhx8pb3w/edit#heading\u003dh.bcu4xguzyf1w for an example.\n\nThis means that in order to update a device reason, an explicit \"device reason update\" call needs to be made instead of wrapping it up with the device structure itself.",
